    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 43-21-151, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REVISE THE EXCLUSIVE ORIGINAL JURISDICTION OF THE YOUTH COURT BY EXCLUDING, FROM SUCH JURISDICTION, AN ACT OF A CHILD WHO KNOWINGLY OR INTENTIONALLY COMMITS POSSESSION OF A STOLEN FIREARM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
